This projects aims to allow users to "skip scenes" on media playback.  It aims to be be an EDL (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edit_decision_list) player for any arbitrary player.

It aims to work with any arbitrary media player (VLC and online players, for example hulu/netflix).


Creating a player description:

  some tips:
  
    run with -v -- it will dump a screenshot of the window in question
    use Paint.net to examine the
    use AutoIt spy to see window names (install AutoHotKey to get it).


Trouble Shooting:

If you have poor performance, possibly set the process priority to low on the DVD player program.
